attributes.long-description:
Forget all the dodge games you have ever played with! Bunny Dodge has arrived to chain you to your device forever!
Our world is falling into pieces! Only this mighty bunny can help to restore the space-time continuum!
Save the world with Smokie! Dodge falling blocks in breathtaking, tricky and challenging mazes!
-Missions to Hawaii, Vegas, Paris, North Dakota and more
-Bounce beach babes, angry chef or shy chicken!
-Collect words for extra gold
-Catch insane falling objects, coins, gems and gold to unlock all the features and levels.
-If you're done become the King of Golden Carrots by mastering the mazes!
-Myriad of clothes to camouflage Smokie, like ninja, soldier, doctor, hula dancer, farmer, lover and so many more
-Take care of your own garden to get fruits that give Smokie extra abilities in missions such as extra life, luck, speed, invulnerability and so on
-Plant! Look after! Harvest...and enjoy!!!
And don`t forget! The Bunny may be with you!!!
